%div.admin-tasks{:style => "overflow: auto"}
  From here you will be able to do things the underprivileged cannot do, such as:
  %ul.admin-task-list
    %li= "Create a #{A('New Paste', :href => "/new")}, without having to get a link from IRC first"
    %li 
      Paste without a web browser. To do so, post a form with the paste_body parameter containing your paste at:
      %pre http://pastr.it/new/NETWORK/CHANNEL/LANGUAGE/TITLE
      or you can use request parameters for network (required),
      channel (required), language or title.  Curl example
      %pre echo "some plain text, piped"|curl --form "paste_body=<-" -F "title=sample text" -0 -no out -L http://pastr.it/new/Freenode/_rubyists/plain%20text
    %li Set up alternate nicknames to recognize you by (not yet implemented)
    %li Get pastr to join (or leave) a channel (not yet implemented)
